### ============================================================
### API SMK NEGERI 3 BALIGE
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api
### Gunakan REST Client extension di VS Code untuk menjalankan
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api


### ============================================================
### 1. SEJARAH & IDENTITAS
### ============================================================

### GET - Ambil semua data sejarah identitas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sejarah-identitas
Content-Type: application/json

###

### GET - Ambil data sejarah identitas by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sejarah-identitas/950e3da6-5bce-4403-b513-7c1282638cb8
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Tambah data sejarah identitas
POST {{baseUrl}}/sejarah-identitas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tahun_berdiri": "1995",
  "deskripsi": "SMK Negeri 3 Balige berdiri sejak tahun 1995 dan telah berkembang menjadi institusi vokasi unggulan yang fokus pada integrasi teknologi informasi dalam setiap aspek pendidikan."
}

###

### PUT - Update data sejarah identitas by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sejarah-identitas/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tahun_berdiri": "1995",
  "deskripsi": "Deskripsi yang telah diperbarui..."
}

###

### DELETE - Hapus data sejarah identitas by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sejarah-identitas/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json


### ============================================================
### 2. VISI & MISI
### ============================================================

### GET - Ambil semua data visi & misi
GET {{baseUrl}}/visi-misi
Content-Type: application/json

###

### GET - Ambil data visi & misi by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/visi-misi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Tambah data VISI
POST {{baseUrl}}/visi-misi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipe": "visi",
  "deskripsi": "Menjadi sekolah unggulan yang menghasilkan lulusan berakhlak mulia, berprestasi, dan berwawasan global pada tahun 2030."
}

###

### POST - Tambah data MISI
POST {{baseUrl}}/visi-misi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipe": "misi",
  "deskripsi": "Mengembangkan potensi siswa secara optimal melalui pembelajaran yang inovatif dan relevan dengan dunia industri."
}

###

### PUT - Update data visi & misi by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/visi-misi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipe": "visi",
  "deskripsi": "Deskripsi visi yang diperbarui..."
}

###

### DELETE - Hapus data visi & misi by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/visi-misi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json


### ============================================================
### 3. STRUKTUR ORGANISASI
### ⚠️  Upload file menggunakan multipart/form-data
###    Ganti path file sesuai lokasi file di komputer kamu
### ============================================================

### GET - Ambil semua data struktur organisasi
GET {{baseUrl}}/struktur-organisasi
Content-Type: application/json

###

### GET - Ambil data struktur organisasi by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/struktur-organisasi/0948ca74-e307-4bf5-a429-32a23fe7c89e
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Upload gambar struktur organisasi
POST {{baseUrl}}/struktur-organisasi
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="gambar"; filename="struktur.png"
Content-Type: image/jpg

< images.jpg

------FormBoundary--

###

### PUT - Update gambar struktur organisasi by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/struktur-organisasi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="gambar"; filename="struktur-baru.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< C:/path/to/gambar-struktur-baru.png

------FormBoundary--

###

### DELETE - Hapus data struktur organisasi by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/struktur-organisasi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json


### ============================================================
### 4. FASILITAS & SARANA BELAJAR
### ⚠️  Upload foto menggunakan multipart/form-data
### ============================================================

### GET - Ambil semua data fasilitas
GET {{baseUrl}}/fasilitas
Content-Type: application/json

###

### GET - Ambil data fasilitas by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/fasilitas/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Tambah fasilitas dengan foto
POST {{baseUrl}}/fasilitas
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama_fasilitas"

Lab Komputer & Jaringan
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Laboratorium komputer dengan 40 unit PC dan koneksi internet berkecepatan tinggi
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="foto"; filename="lab-komputer.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< C:/path/to/foto-fasilitas.png

------FormBoundary--

###

### POST - Tambah fasilitas tanpa foto
POST {{baseUrl}}/fasilitas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama_fasilitas": "Lapangan Olahraga",
  "deskripsi": "Lapangan olahraga serbaguna untuk kegiatan ekstrakurikuler"
}

###

### PUT - Update fasilitas by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/fasilitas/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama_fasilitas": "Lab Komputer & Jaringan (Updated)",
  "deskripsi": "Deskripsi yang diperbarui"
}

###

### DELETE - Hapus data fasilitas by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fasilitas/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json


### ============================================================
### 5. AKREDITASI & PRESTASI
### ============================================================

### GET - Ambil semua data prestasi
GET {{baseUrl}}/prestasi
Content-Type: application/json

###

### GET - Ambil data prestasi by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/prestasi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Tambah data prestasi
POST {{baseUrl}}/prestasi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "judul": "Juara I LKS Bidang Electronic Application",
  "tingkat": "provinsi",
  "tahun": "2023",
  "keterangan": "Lomba Kompetensi Siswa Tingkat Provinsi Sumatera Utara"
}

###

### POST - Tambah prestasi tingkat nasional
POST {{baseUrl}}/prestasi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "judul": "Juara II LKS Bidang Automobile Technology",
  "tingkat": "nasional",
  "tahun": "2022",
  "keterangan": "Lomba Kompetensi Siswa Tingkat Nasional"
}

###

### PUT - Update data prestasi by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/prestasi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "judul": "Judul prestasi yang diperbarui",
  "tingkat": "nasional",
  "tahun": "2024"
}

###

### DELETE - Hapus data prestasi by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/prestasi/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json


