### ============================================================
### 7. MITRA KERJASAMA
### ⚠️  Upload logo menggunakan multipart/form-data
### ============================================================

### GET - Ambil semua mitra kerjasama
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra-kerjasama
Content-Type: application/json

###

### GET - Ambil data mitra kerjasama by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/mitra-kerjasama/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Tambah mitra dengan logo
POST {{baseUrl}}/mitra-kerjasama
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nama_mitra"

PT. PLN (Persero)
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deskripsi"

Perusahaan listrik negara
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="pln-logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< C:/path/to/logo-mitra.png

------FormBoundary--

###

### POST - Tambah mitra tanpa logo
POST {{baseUrl}}/mitra-kerjasama
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama_mitra": "PT. Telkom Indonesia",
  "deskripsi": "Perusahaan telekomunikasi nasional"
}

###

### PUT - Update mitra kerjasama by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/mitra-kerjasama/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama_mitra": "PT. PLN (Persero) Updated",
  "deskripsi": "Deskripsi yang diperbarui"
}

###

### DELETE - Hapus mitra kerjasama by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/mitra-kerjasama/isi-id-disini
Content-Type: application/json
